        <p>The coastal strip from Huntington Beach through Newport to Dana Point has the same salt air challenge we see in Santa Monica — coil corrosion and gasket wear happen on a 4–6 month cycle, not 12. Our Irvine branch at (213) 401-9019 gives us faster response across the county than a company dispatching from LA.</p>
        <p>Orange County also has specific commercial needs — the restaurant density near the Anaheim Convention Center, the hotel concentration in Newport Beach and Dana Point, and the retail corridors in Costa Mesa's South Coast Plaza area. Same day appliance repair in Orange County covers both residential and commercial across all 14 cities.</p></div>
