        <p>Newport Beach and Laguna Beach sit right on the water — salt air effects on appliances are significant and fast. Condenser coils corrode, door gaskets dry and crack, and refrigerators that would last 14 years inland need coil attention every 6 months at the coast.</p>
        <p>Inland cities like Yorba Linda, Anaheim, and Fullerton have summer temperatures that push refrigeration hard. The housing here is largely suburban single-family — Whirlpool, GE, and Maytag in homes built 1970–2000. Repair makes strong economic sense for these units. Same day appliance repair in Orange County means knowing this difference before we arrive.</p>
